  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "AES-256-CBC de-obfuscation engine for secure device secrets at boot time. Decrypts obfuscated UDS (Unique Device Secret), Field Entropy, and HEK (Hardware Embedded Key) using a shared obfuscation key, writing results directly to KeyVault. Features flow locking (one-shot per boot) and zeroize capability. AHB-Lite slave interface. Extracted from CHIPS Alliance Caliptra Root of Trust.",
