    ]
  },
  "architecture": {
    "type": "peripheral",
    "features": [
      "AES-256-CBC encryption and decryption",
      "De-obfuscation of UDS (128-bit), Field Entropy (128-bit), HEK (256-bit)",
      "IV chaining for CBC mode (auto-update per block)",
      "Flow locking: UDS_FLOW_DONE, FE_FLOW_DONE, HEK_FLOW_DONE (one-shot per boot)",
      "KeyVault write for secure secret storage",
      "OCP lock awareness for HEK operations",
      "Zeroize command to clear obfuscated secrets",
      "Forward and inverse S-Box (4x parallel, 256-byte ROM)",
      "AES key expansion memory (10/14 rounds for 128/256-bit keys)",
      "Separate encipher and decipher datapaths",
      "PeakRDL-generated register file"
    ]
  },
